    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Promissio de suprascripta cartula. In nomine domini Dei eterni. Anno ab
                        incarnatione eius millesimo quinquagesimo septimo, tertio idus martii,
                        indictione VIIIa. Manifestus sum ego <persName><name ref="Heinricus"
                                >Enrigo</name></persName> filius bone memorie <persName><name
                                ref="Rotius">Rothi</name></persName> quia tu <persName
                            key="#Priests"><name ref="Liudus">Liudo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> filius bone memorie <persName><name
                                ref="Liutfredus">Liufredi</name></persName> dedisti mihi argentum
                        solidos centum, propterea per hanc repromissionis paginam mea bona
                        spontaneaque voluntate, repromitto tibi ut da admodum in antea nullo tempore
                        non appareat nullo meo datum neque factum qui ego qui supra Enrigo factum
                        habea[m] aut in antea faciam de integre due portionis de due <rs
                            key="#Petiae">petias</rs> de terra, una qui dicitur a <placeName
                            key="#Petiae #Wine" ref="#places/87">Valli</placeName>, cum <rs
                            key="#Wine">vinea</rs> super se habentem, alia a <placeName
                            key="#Petiae" ref="#places/149">Monticelli</placeName>, qui ego Henrigo
                        per cartula dedi Liudi presbiteri. Si apparuerit ullum meum datum vel factum
                        qui ego fatum abeam aut in antea faciam per nullum argumentis ingenium,
                        componam ego qui supra Enrigo Liudi presbitero vel a suo herede penam
                        numerum argentum solidos C. Et ita in hoc ordine ac promissio <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Walpertus">Walberto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notario</rs> domni inperatoris scribere rogavi. Actum loco
                            <placeName key="#Castle" ref="#places/148">Sasso</placeName> ad ipso <rs
                            key="#Castle">castello</rs>, <rs key="#Comitatus">territorio</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/107">Vulterrense</geogName>. Signum
                        manus suprascripti Enrigi qui hanc promissio fieri rogavit. Signa manuum
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Gherardus">Gerardi</name></persName>
                        filii bone memorie <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Winizo">Winitj</name></persName>
                        filii bone memorie <persName><name ref="Cicius">Cici</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Rusticus">Rustici</name></persName>
                        filii <persName><name ref="Teutius">Teutj</name></persName> testium.
                        Walberto notarius post tradita complevi et dedi. </ab>
                </div>
